\doxysubsubsection{\texorpdfstring{check\_menu\_click()}{check\_menu\_click()}}
{\footnotesize\ttfamily int check\+\_\+menu\+\_\+click (\begin{DoxyParamCaption}\item[{SDL\+\_\+\+Point}]{mouse\+Pos }\end{DoxyParamCaption})}



Checks if a mouse click occurred on any menu button. 

Iterates through all buttons to see if the click position intersects with any button\textquotesingle{}s rectangle. Returns the index of the clicked button or -\/1 if no button was clicked.


\begin{DoxyParams}{Parameters}
{\em mouse\+Pos} & The position of the mouse click. \\
\hline
\end{DoxyParams}
\begin{DoxyReturn}{Returns}
Index of the clicked button (0-\/4) or -\/1 if none. 
\end{DoxyReturn}
